data.title: Opinion, knowledge, and clinical experience with functional neurological disorders among Italian neurologists: results from an online survey
data.meta_description: Overall, the responses suggest that knowledge about scientific advances in FND is somewhat sparse. A psychiatric-centered view of FND opens the way to an approach in which neurobiological and psychological aspects constitute essential factors of the condition.
